        "sourceId": "tool_response_call_JDLXx1NJjhlazJWBOCaGpFCN",
        "executionId": "call_JDLXx1NJjhlazJWBOCaGpFCN",
        "result": {
          "success": true,
          "data": "### Café Menu\n\n#### Beverage Options\n\n1. **Iced Matcha Latte**  \n   - **Description**: A refreshing blend of high-quality matcha green tea whisked with creamy oat milk and served over ice. Sweetened with a hint of agave syrup for a smooth finish.  \n   - **Price**: $5.50  \n\n2. **Lavender Lemonade Spritzer**  \n   - **Description**: A vibrant, floral-infused lemonade topped with sparkling water and garnished with fresh lavender sprigs. Perfect for a sunny day!  \n   - **Price**: $4.00  \n\n3. **Coconut Cold Brew**  \n   - **Description**: Smooth, rich cold brew coffee mixed with coconut cream and served over ice. A delicious dairy-free option that’s both energizing and refreshing.  \n   - **Price**: $5.00  \n\n#### Dessert Options\n\n1. **Vegan Chocolate Avocado Mousse**  \n   - **Description**: A rich and creamy dessert made from ripe avocados, high-quality cocoa powder, and maple syrup. Topped with fresh berries and a sprinkle of sea salt.  \n   - **Price**: $6.00  \n\n2. **Brownie Sundae Parfait**  \n   - **Description**: Layers of fudgy brownie chunks, vanilla ice cream, and chocolate sauce, topped with whipped cream and toasted pecans. A decadent treat for chocolate lovers!  \n   - **Price**: $7.00  \n\n---\n\n### Notes:  \n- **Trends**: The beverage options reflect a growing interest in plant-based and health-conscious choices, while the desserts offer indulgence alongside vegan options to cater to a wider audience.\n- **Target Audience**: The menu is designed to attract health-conscious individuals, young professionals, and dessert lovers, appealing to current café trends focusing on quality ingredients and unique flavor combinations.\n- **Competitive Pricing**: Prices are set to ensure accessibility while maintaining quality, in line with similar offerings in the local market."
        },
